latestPosts.caption:
Memorable day 🙏🏻💛

I’ve always dreamed of giving back a small surprise to my parents and in-laws, who spent their lives making ours magical. 

They sacrificed everything for our happiness, they used to surprise us by midnight cakes,our fav toys and many more.., never wanting anything in return. So, my husband and I planned a surprise to make their eyes sparkle - their first flight to Shirdi! 

Seeing them thrilled, a little nervous, and completely surprised is pure joy 🥹 This will be a core memory for us to treasure. 🥹

This might look like a tiny thing and yes I live for these tiny moments in life 😇

#blessedandgrateful #thankful #haraharamahadev #omsairam
